:"麻弥","body":"我们Pastel＊Palettes是在东京活动的偶像组合。\n今天要巡游佐贺各地，\n介绍非常多佐贺的好地方！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event154-03-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"首先我们来到了这里，嬉野温泉的足浴池。\n一大早就已经有很多客人来泡了呢。\n大家看起来都很享受！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event154-03-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千圣","body":"那我们去采访一下正在泡足浴的客人吧。\n请问觉得这温泉怎么样？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event154-03-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":221}],"windowDisplayName":"巽","body":"呀，这温泉的水温正好。\n不仅仅是让身心都温暖起来，就连肌肤都变得湿润嫩滑。\n真不愧是日本三大美肤温泉之一呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":221,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":221,"voiceId":"event154-03-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"wind